high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the fridge, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the large metal knife out of the sink.
Slice up the apple that is closest to the faucet in the sink.
Put the large metal knife into the sink.
Pick up a piece of sliced apple.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Microwave the piece of sliced apple for a couple seconds to heat it up, then pick it back up.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the heated piece of sliced apple into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of sliced apple in the sink.

high_descs: turn around, go to sink to the right
pick up yellow handle knife to the right of apples in sink
slice apple in back of sink
place knife in sink
pick up slice of apple from sink
turn right to counter with microwave
place apple slice on gray plate in microwave, microwave apple slice, take apple slice out of microwave, close microwave
turn left, go to sink
place apple slice in right side of sink
anns.task_desc: place microwaved apple slice in sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the sink.
Pick the knife up from the sink.
Slice the apple in the back of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn to the right to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the piece of apple up again.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed piece of apple in a sink.
